<abstract>
<para>This data set contains meausrements of soil properties (soil moisture, soil temperature, thaw depth) of sites surrounding an eddy covariance tower. The purpose was to see how physical changes in the lanscape effect carbon fluxes measurede by the EC tower.</para>
